  "full_ocr_markdown": "# Page 1\n\n# Atlantic Capital Partners VII, L.P.\n## Quarterly Report - Q3 2024\n### For the Period Ending September 30, 2024\n\n## Fund Summary\n\n**Fund ID:** ACP-VII\n\n**Total Commitments:** $1,200,000,000\n\n**Capital Called to Date:** $890,000,000\n\n**Cumulative Distributions:** $412,000,000\n\n**Net Asset Value:** $823,000,000\n\n## Schedule of Investments\n\nAs of September 30, 2024, the Fund held investments in 12 portfolio companies:\n\n| Portfolio Company | Industry | Investment Date | Cost Basis | Fair Value |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Nexus Semiconductor Corp | Semiconductors | Jan 2020 | $78,000,000 | $142,000,000 |\n| UrbanSpace Real Estate Tech | PropTech | Apr 2020 | $45,000,000 | $67,500,000 |\n| Precision Instruments Ltd | Medical Devices | Jul 2020 | $52,000,000 | $71,000,000 |\n| CyberGuard Networks | Cybersecurity | Oct 2020 | $41,000,000 | $58,200,000 |\n| AutoDrive Systems | Automotive Tech | Jan 2021 | $95,000,000 | $68,000,000 |\n| PaymentHub International | Fintech | Apr 2021 | $63,000,000 | $94,500,000 |\n| AgriTech Innovations | Agriculture Tech | Jul 2021 | $38,000,000 | $45,600,000 |\n| StreamMedia Entertainment | Digital Media | Oct 2021 | $55,000,000 | $42,000,000 |\n| NanoMaterials Inc | Advanced Materials | Jan 2022 | $47,000,000 | $52,800,000 |\n| HealthFirst Clinics | Healthcare Services | Apr 2022 | $72,000,000 | $89,000,000 |\n| EdgeAI Computing | Artificial Intelligence | Jul 2022 | $58,000,000 | $78,400,000 |\n| SecureVault Storage | Data Infrastructure | Oct 2022 | $34,000,000 | $14,000,000 |\n| **TOTAL** | | | **$678,000,000** | **$823,000,000** |\n\n---\n\n# Page 2\n\n# Performance Metrics\n\nTVPI (Total Value to Paid-In): 1.39x\nDPI (Distributions to Paid-In): 0.46x\nRVPI (Residual Value to Paid-In): 0.92x\n\n**CONFIDENTIAL - FOR LIMITED PARTNER USE ONLY**\n\nThis quarterly report is provided for informational purposes only. Fair values are estimated based on the General Partner's assessment and 